Class UserRoleAssignmentDelegate

  • entity.UserRoleAssignmentDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assignable, Bean

    public class UserRoleAssignmentDelegate
implements Bean, Assignable
    Represents the assignment of a role to a user on an assignable object.
